      <title>कृष्णयजुर्वेदिषु</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/kalpAntaram/dharmaH/nibandhaH/vishvAsaH/kriyA-nishchayaH/sandhyAvandanam/kyv/</link>
