d=&#34;उततरङगण&#34;&gt;उत्तराङ्गाणि&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;उपस्थानम्&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;अभिवादनम्&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;उपसथनम&#34;&gt;उपस्थानम्&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;false&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;../../../../../mantraH/misc-devas/yajuH/sUrya-iva-dRshe/&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;false&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;../../../../../mantraH/AdityaH/Rk/adya_no_deva/&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
